ul.li:
To figure out how the elements are mapped into PDF, you can use this
          fragment in the customization
          CSS:* {
   border: 1pt solid blue !important;
}

*:before(1000) {
   content:  oxy_name() !important;
   color: orange;
}

*:before(999) {
   content: "[ class= '" attr(class) "'] " !important;
   color: orange;
}This will show the element name, its class attribute, and will paint a blue
          border around each of the elements in the output. It will not show the page margin boxes
          or some content elements that are hidden.
